## StringEncoding.name property

The canonical name of this [StringEncoding](./iconv-corefoundation.stringencoding.md)<!-- -->. This is likely (but not guaranteed) to be a unique identifier for each distinct encoding.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
readonly name: string;
```

## Remarks

This is the return value of the Core Foundation function [CFStringGetNameOfEncoding](https://developer.apple.com/documentation/corefoundation/1543585-cfstringgetnameofencoding?language=objc)<!-- -->.
